::Battera::

She looked around.  She fnished her apple and tossed the core away in 
the trash.  She started eating a peach.  She hoped the leader of this 
group would call on her soon so she could speak her case.  She 
started thinking of Cybershark.  She hoped he was having better luck 
thatn she was.  Turned her head around and looked at the empty room. 
She sighed. She was beginnning to feel like she was failing at her 
mission.  She was feeling like this was would never end. That is 
would go on forever. She got a scent going by the room. Firearm, 
that's who it reminded her of.  She looked but no one was around.

She got up, still nibling on the peach.  She picked up three more 
apples and decided to walk over to the bridge. She figured she had 
found bots there every other time she went to the bridge, why should 
this time be different.  If she found someone, she at least could ask 
to see if the leader had arrived yet.  She strolled down the hallway 
towards the bridge.
